#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kdeconnect.metainfo.xml:6
msgid "KDE Connect"
msgstr "KDE Connect"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kdeconnect.metainfo.xml:7
msgid "Seamless connection of your devices"
msgstr "Nasc gan uaim do ghléasanna"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdeconnect.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"KDE Connect makes your phone and computer work better together: share your "
"clipboard and access files across devices, turn your phone into a remote "
"control for your computer, find your phone when it has slipped down the back "
"of your couch, see your phone notifications from your computer, and much "
"more!"
msgstr ""
"Déanann KDE Connect do ghuthán agus do ríomhaire a oibriú níos fearr le "
"chéile: roinn do ghearrthaisce agus rochtain a fháil ar chomhaid trasna "
"gléasanna, déan cianrialtán do do ríomhaire de do ghuthán, aimsigh do "
"ghuthán nuair a shleamhnaigh sé síos cúl do tholg, féach fógraí do ghutháin "
"ó do ríomhaire, agus i bhfad níos mó!"
